titles.title: A resolution agreeing to the conference requested by the Senate on the bill H.R. 5261.

action.text: Called up by House Under Suspension of Rules.
Resolution Agreed to in House by Yea-Nay Vote: 397 - 20 (Record Vote No: 416).

bill.summary: 10/3/1988--Introduced. Provides for taking from the Speaker's table H.R. 5261 (Indian health care), with Senate amendments thereto, disagreeing with the Senate amendments, and agreeing to the conference requested by the Senate.
